"{\"uid\": \"kbtx.com-2024-07-29-paris-2024-texas-am-athletes-aim-olympic-glory\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"COLLEGE STATION, Texas (KBTX) -Texas A&M is looking to make a strong showing at the 2024 Paris Olympics with 24 former and current athletes competing.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 150, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 17, \"end\": 22, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas_Longhorns\", \"score\": 0.9886962881562339, \"rank\": 0.005994638538793763, \"text\": \"Texas\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas_Longhorns\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas_Longhorns\"}, {\"begin\": 24, \"end\": 28, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KBTX-TV\", \"score\": 0.9999999999643023, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"KBTX\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KBTX-TV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KBTX-TV\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Among them is Maggie Malone-Hardin, who is making her third Olympic appearance in the javelin.\", \"from\": 152, \"to\": 246, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 166, \"end\": 172, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maggie_Greene\", \"score\": 0.9374267935166276, \"rank\": 0.06283000491011331, \"text\": \"Maggie\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maggie_Greene\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maggie_Greene\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Malone-Hardin holds the American record in javelin and has earned multiple All-American honors during her collegiate career.\", \"from\": 248, \"to\": 372, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 272, \"end\": 280, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9997008953050261, \"rank\": 0.0002527636961821928, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 323, \"end\": 335, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/All-America\", \"score\": 0.9990290170407107, \"rank\": 0.0006804894531874469, \"text\": \"All-American\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/All-America\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/All-America\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am really grateful just to get to compete one more time and take the experience that I had from the last two and pull it into this third one and overall know that my worth is not in the medal that I may or may not receive or on the number that comes up on the screen, but it's in Jesus at the end of the day,\\\" said Malone-Hardin.\", \"from\": 374, \"to\": 706, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 657, \"end\": 662, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.7239519459308822, \"rank\": 0.38130545796941445, \"text\": \"Jesus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Malone-Hardin says her journey has been marked by perseverance and faith.\", \"from\": 708, \"to\": 781, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I can not believe that I am still a part of this and thinking back to 2016, my very first Olympic Games, and just the person that I was then versus where I am at now.\", \"from\": 783, \"to\": 950, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have a lot of compassion and a lot of grace for that version of Maggie in 2016,\\\" Malone-Hardin added.\", \"from\": 951, \"to\": 1054, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1017, \"end\": 1023, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maggie_Greene\", \"score\": 0.9374267935166276, \"rank\": 0.06283000491011331, \"text\": \"Maggie\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maggie_Greene\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maggie_Greene\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Shaine Casas is making his first Olympic appearance and is known for his versatility in the pool, setting multiple NCAA records.\", \"from\": 1056, \"to\": 1184, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1056, \"end\": 1068, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shaine_Casas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Shaine Casas\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shaine_Casas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shaine_Casas\"}, {\"begin\": 1171, \"end\": 1175, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Collegiate_Athletic_Association\", \"score\": 0.9964768334831967, \"rank\": 0.0035325312505672286, \"text\": \"NCAA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Collegiate_Athletic_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Collegiate_Athletic_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have been doing my best to be as prepared and as fit and ready for this moment.\", \"from\": 1186, \"to\": 1268, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And you know if I can kind of give everything I have got and execute, I do not think leaving with a medal is outside of my capabilities,\\\" said Casas.\", \"from\": 1269, \"to\": 1418, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Casas says while he is excited to be in Paris, he's focused on living in the moment and enjoying his Olympic experience to the fullest.\", \"from\": 1420, \"to\": 1555, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1460, \"end\": 1465, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999953970351706, \"rank\": 4.602985926440893e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Even if you make it again, it might not be the same thing and the same experience.\", \"from\": 1557, \"to\": 1640, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The first time is probably the most intense and overwhelming and memorable of all.\", \"from\": 1641, \"to\": 1723, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am hoping that this first one is awesome.\", \"from\": 1724, \"to\": 1767, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I hope to have more in the future, but my biggest thing is being present,\\\" said Casas  Casas is set to compete in the Men's 200m Individual Medley on Thursday.\", \"from\": 1768, \"to\": 1927, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The women's javelin throw qualifying rounds are on August 7.\", \"from\": 1928, \"to\": 1988, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Copyright 2024 KBTX.\", \"from\": 1990, \"to\": 2010, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All rights reserved.\", \"from\": 2011, \"to\": 2031, \"entities\": []}]}"